title: Mike Cheese from Gehenna
itunes:title: Mike Cheese from Gehenna
description:
I was able to catch up with an old friend and vocalist for the metal/punk band Gehenna. We spoke about music as a medium, artistic expression and what it's like to live in your car for months at a time. A very deep conversation that will appeal to anyone who is a fan of music in general. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
